<br>
Today, following links from news sites (sadly 2 died when an historic clock tower collapsed and possibly 1 other death elsewhere), I found a nifty site which has created an animation from the USGS maps... way spiffy: <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.classicalarchives.com/eq/">Earthquake Animations</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> (the other EQ *smirk*)<br>
<br>
