<br>
When I lived in California, I <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>loved</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> earthquakes.  But I was a teenager at the time.  It was fun for me to watch the pool making waves and everything in my room flying all over, etc.  I honestly was not scared in the least, it was exhilirating and awe-inspiring.<br>
<br>
